Package: ZarrExperiment
Title: Manipulate Zarr archives as R objects
Description: The ZarrExperiment package defines the ZarrExperiment class,
    an interface between the zarr format and functionality and Biocondcutor's
    "Experiment" class. It also defines a set of wrappers for zarr's python
    wrappers. It allows remote representations from an S3-like location with
    the ZarrRemote class.
